Cherry Blossoms;;91;;79;;NC;;Learning that her husband, Rudi (Elmar Wepper), has a terminal illness, Trudi (Hannelore Elsner) hides the knowledge from him and persuades him to visit their son in Japan. During the course of their journey, she dies in her sleep -- before telling Rudi of his impending death. Grief-stricken, he continues on toward Japan, finally finding peace at Mount Fuji.;;Drama;;Doris Dörrie;;2008;;Elmar Wepper,Hannelore Elsner,Aya Irizuki,Maximilian Brückner,Nadja Uhl,Birgit Minichmayr,Felix Eitner,Floriane Daniel,Celine Tanneberger;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cherry_blossoms_hanami